<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197606>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Casuarinicola australis sp. nov. (1), habitus, female (dorsal aspect); (2), habitus, male (dorsal aspect); (3), habitus female (lateral aspect); (4), habitus male (lateral aspect); (5), fore wing, female; (6), fore wing, male; (7), head (dorsal aspect). Scale = 0.5 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197606/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197607>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 11. Casuarinicola australis sp. nov. (8), male terminalia (lateral aspect); (9), paramere (inner face, lateral aspect); (10), female terminalia, (lateral aspect); (11), fifth (final) instar nymph (ventral aspect, left; dorsal aspect right). Scale = 0.2 mm Figs 8 – 10, 0.5 mm Fig. 11." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197607/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.197614>
    dc:description "FIGURES 50 – 51. Distribution for Australian species of Casuarinicola gen. nov.: (50),, Casuarinicola australis sp. nov.; (51),, C. nigrimaculatus sp. nov.;, C. mucronalatus sp. nov.;, C. warrigalensis sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/197614/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

